        TarotCard(id: 29, name: "Eight of Wands", arcana: .minor, suit: .wands, number: "8",
            uprightMeaning: "Eight wands fly through the open sky without obstruction — this is the card of swift action, rapid communication, and momentum unencumbered by doubt. What has been stalled suddenly moves. The message arrives. The journey begins. Do not stand in the way of your own velocity.",
