            uprightMeaning: "A young explorer holds a wand and gazes at a distant landscape with pure, unfiltered enthusiasm. The Page of Wands brings news of adventure, the energy of pure possibility, and the permission to approach something entirely new with beginners' mind — to explore without needing to be expert.",
